quran[70]{c,v,t}:
  69,1,"Honi shudhni ! (indubitable) [sach-much honay wali]"
  69,2,Kya hai woh honi shudni (indubitable)
  69,3,Aur tum kya jaano ke woh kya hai honi shudhni (indubitable)
  69,4,Samood aur Aad ne us achanak toot padne wali aafat ko jhutlaya
  69,5,To Samood ek sakht haadse mein halaaq kiye gaye
  69,6,Aur Aad ek badi shadeed toofani aandhi(storm) se tabah kardiye gaye
  69,7,Allah taala ne usko musalsal saat (seven) raat aur aath (eight) din unpar musallat rakkha (tum wahan hotey to) dekhte ke woh wahan is tarah pachade paday jaise woh khajoor ke boseeda (rotten) taney (trunks) hon
  69,8,Ab kya unmein se koi tumhein baki nazar aata hai
  69,9,Aur isi khata-e-azeem ka irtiqaab Firoun aur ussey pehle ke logon ne aur talpat (overturned) ho janey wali bastiyon ne kiya
  69,10,Un sab ne apne Rubb ke Rasool ki baat na maani to usne unko bade sakhti ke saath pakda
  69,11,Jab pani ka toofan hadd se guzar gaya to humne tumko kashti mein sawar kardiya tha
  69,12,Taa-ke is waqiye ko tumhare liye ek sabaq-aamoz yaadgaar bana dein aur yaad rakhne waley kaan iski yaad mehfooz rakkhein
  69,13,Phir jab ek dafa sur mein phoonk maar di jayegi
  69,14,Aur zameen aur pahadon ko utha kar ek hi chot mein reza reza kardiya jayega
  69,15,Us roz woh honay wala waqiya pesh aa jayega
  69,16,Usdin Aasmaan phatega aur uski bandish dhili padh jayegi
  69,17,Farishtey uske atraf-o-jawanib mein hongey aur aat (eight) farishtey us roz tere Rubb ka arsh apne upar uthaye huey hongey
  69,18,"Woh din hoga jab tumlog pesh kiye jaogey, tumhara koi raaz bhi chupa na reh jayega"
  69,19,"Us waqt jiska naam-e-aamal uske seedhey haath mein diya jayega woh kahega “lo dekho, padho mera naam-e-aamal"
  69,20,Main samajhta tha ke mujhey zaroor apna hisaab milne wala hai”
  69,21,Pas woh dil pasand aish mein hoga
  69,22,Aali muqaam jannat mein
  69,23,Jiske phalon ke guchhey jhuke padh rahey hongey
  69,24,(Aise logon se kaha jayega) mazey se khao aur pio apne un aamal ke badle jo tumne guzre huey dino mein kiye hain
  69,25,Aur jiska naam-e-aamal uske bayein (left) haath mein diya jayega woh kahega “ kaash mera aamal nama mujhey na diya gaya hota
  69,26,Aur main na jaanta ke mera hisaab kya hai
  69,27,Kaash meri wahi maut (jo duniya mei aayi thi) faisla-kun hoti
  69,28,Aaj mera maal mere kuch kaam na aaya
  69,29,Mera sara iqtedaar khatam ho gaya
  69,30,(hukum hoga) pakdo isey aur iski gardan mei touk daal do
  69,31,Phir isey jahannum mein jhoonk do
  69,32,Phir isko satter(seventy) haath lambi zanjeer mei jakad do
  69,33,Yeh na Allah buzurg-o-bartar par iman lata tha
  69,34,Aur na miskeen ko khana khilane ki targeeb deta tha
  69,35,Lihaza aaj na yahan iska koi yaar-e-gamkhaar hai
  69,36,Aur na zakhmon ke dhowan (washing of wounds) ke siwa iske liye koi khana
  69,37,Jisey khatakaaron (sinners) ke siwa koi nahin khata
  69,38,"Pas nahin, main qasam khata hoon un cheezon ki bhi jo tum dekhte ho"
  69,39,Aur unki bhi jinhein tum nahin dekhte
  69,40,Yeh ek Rasool-e-kareem ka qaul ( speech ) hai
  69,41,"Kisi shayar ka qaul nahin hai, tumlog kam hi iman latey ho"
  69,42,"Aur na yeh kisi kaahin(soothsayer) ka qaul hai , tum log kam hi gaur karte ho"
  69,43,Yeh Rabb-ul alameen ki taraf se nazil huwa hai
  69,44,Aur agar is (Nabi) ne khud ghad kar koi baat hamari taraf mansook ki hoti
  69,45,To hum iska dayan(right) haath padkad letay
  69,46,Aur iski rag-e-gardan (life vein) kaat daalte
  69,47,Phir tum mein se koi (humein)is kaam se rokne wala na hota
  69,48,Dar haqeeqat yeh parheizgar logon ke liye ek naseehat hai
  69,49,Aur hum jante hain ke tum mein se kuch log jhutlane waley hain
  69,50,Aise kafiron ke liye yaqeenan yeh mujeeb-e-hasrat (cause of regret) hai
  69,51,Aur yeh bilkul yaqeeni haqq hai
  69,52,"Pas aey nabi, apne Rubb-e-azeem ke naam ki tasbeeh karo"
  70,1,Mangne waley ne azaab maanga hai (woh azaab) jo zaroor waqey honay wala hai
  70,2,"Kafiron ke liye hai, koi usey dafa karne wala nahin"
  70,3,Us khuda ki taraf se hai jo urooj ke zeeno (ascending steps)ka malik hai
  70,4,Malaika (angels) aur rooh(Jibrael) uske huzoor chadh kar jatey hain ek aise din mein jiski miqdar pacchas (fifty) hazar saal hai
  70,5,"Pas aey Nabi, sabr karo, shaista sabr"
  70,6,Yeh log usey dur samajhte hain
  70,7,Aur hum usey qareeb dekh rahey hain
  70,8,(woh azaab us roz hoga) jis roz aasman pigli huye chandi ki tarah ho jayega
  70,9,Aur pahad rang-bi-rang ke dhunke huey oon (wool) jaise ho jayenge
  70,10,Aur koi jigri dost apne jigri dost ko na puchega
  70,11,"Halaanke woh ek dusre ko dikhaye jayenge, mujrim chahega ke us din ke azaab se bachne ke liye apni aulad ko"
  70,12,"Apni biwi ko, apne bhai ko"
  70,13,Apne qareeb-tareen khandaan ko jo usey panaah dene wala tha
  70,14,Aur rooh-e-zameen ke sab logon ko fidiya (badle) mein dey-de aur yeh tadbeer usey nijaat dila de
  70,15,Hargiz nahin woh to bhadakti hui aag ki lapat hogi
  70,16,Jo gosht posht ko chaat jayegi
  70,17,Pukar pukar kar apni taraf bulayegi har us shaks ko jisne haqq se mooh moda aur peet pheri
  70,18,Aur maal jamaa kiya aur seint seint kar (amassed wealth) rakkha